of Cris searching the place for clues until he&nbsp;
finds Liz with the leader of the terrorists.&nbsp;

00:07:26.000 --> 00:07:30.000
When Cris confronts the leader, he tells him&nbsp;
that he has seen all possible outcomes and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:34.880
none have been in his favor. Therefore, he&nbsp;
